Additional Notice:

This repository contains the open-source scoring algorithm (v1) for the HumanLayer Protocol.
While the algorithm is fully open under MIT, the official HumanLayer implementation on Base may evolve over time based on real-world data, security considerations, and community feedback.

## Important Notes

- This is **v1** of the scoring algorithm.
- We strongly encourage auditing, feedback, and contributions.
- The official deployed version on Base may diverge in the future as we add multi-source attestations and ZK proofs.
- Using this algorithm in your own projects is allowed and encouraged, but claiming to be "HumanLayer" or using our branding is not.
